---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonial Widget for SaaS — SocialProof" description="Turn your happiest users into your best sales asset. SocialProof collects, moderates, and embeds real customer testimonials on your SaaS landing page — no dev work required." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/saas">
<style>

    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .stat-strip { background: #f5f3ff; padding: 32px 24px; }
    .stat-inner { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .stat { }
    .stat-num { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #6c47ff; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; margin-top: 4px; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-section > p { text-align: center; color: #555; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .usecase-strip { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 48px; text-align: center; }
    .usecase-strip p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #888; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; }
    .tag { background: #f0ecff; color: #6c47ff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .steps-section { background: #f5f3ff; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .steps-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .steps-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: left; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .vs-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .vs-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .vs-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .vs-table th { text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; background: #f9f9f9; color: #555; font-weight: 600; }
    .vs-table td { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #333; }
    .vs-table td.vouch { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .vs-table td.them { color: #dc2626; }
    .quote-section { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 auto 16px; max-width: 600px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 18px 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-cta { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #6c47ff; text-decoration: none; }
    footer { padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.875rem; color: #aaa; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
  
</style>
<section class="hero">
    <h1>Social proof that actually converts SaaS visitors into trials</h1>
    <p>Your happiest users are your strongest salespeople. SocialProof makes it easy to collect their words and display them where it counts — on your pricing page, homepage, and feature pages.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register">Start free — no credit card</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="/#demo">See it live</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="stat-strip">
    <div class="stat-inner">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">92%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">of SaaS buyers read reviews before trialing</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">34%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">higher trial conversion with testimonials near CTA</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">5 min</div>
        <div class="stat-label">to add your first testimonial widget</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="usecase-strip">
    <p style="margin-top: 40px;">Works for every kind of SaaS</p>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">B2B SaaS</span>
      <span class="tag">Developer tools</span>
      <span class="tag">Productivity apps</span>
      <span class="tag">Marketing software</span>
      <span class="tag">Analytics platforms</span>
      <span class="tag">HR &amp; hiring tools</span>
      <span class="tag">Fintech</span>
      <span class="tag">No-code builders</span>
      <span class="tag">AI tools</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="why-section">
    <h2>Why SaaS teams use SocialProof</h2>
    <p>G2, Capterra, and Trustpilot collect reviews on <em>their</em> platform. SocialProof puts testimonials on <em>yours</em> — exactly where prospects are deciding.</p>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🎯 Place them where decisions happen</h3>
        <p>Pricing page, feature pages, trial CTA — drop the widget anywhere with one script tag. No engineering ticket needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🔗 Your own collection link</h3>
        <p>Share a link after onboarding or at the 30-day mark. Users click, type their testimonial, done. No survey fatigue, no back-and-forth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>✅ Moderate before it goes live</h3>
        <p>Every testimonial is pending until you approve. You control what shows — keep it accurate and on-brand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>🎨 Matches your design system</h3>
        <p>The widget inherits your brand colors. No "Powered by [Third Party]" badges polluting your carefully designed UI.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>📊 See what's working (Pro)</h3>
        <p>Analytics show which testimonials get seen and on which pages — so you can move the strongest ones to the highest-converting spots.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <h3>⭐ Google rich results (Pro)</h3>
        <p>Structured data markup makes your testimonials eligible for star ratings in Google search results — organic trust at scale.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="steps-section">
    <div class="steps-inner">
      <h2>Live on your pricing page in 3 steps</h2>
      <div class="steps-list">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Sign up and copy your collection link</h3>
            <p>Your link is ready the moment you register. No setup required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Send it to your best users</h3>
            <p>Email it after onboarding, add it to your 30-day check-in, or include it in your NPS survey follow-up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Embed the widget — one script tag</h3>
            <p>Paste one line of HTML. Works on any stack: React, Next.js, Webflow, HTML, Framer. Done.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="vs-section">
    <h2>SocialProof vs. review platforms</h2>
    <table class="vs-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Feature</th>
          <th>SocialProof</th>
          <th>G2 / Capterra</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Testimonials on <em>your</em> site</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ Yes</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Hosted on their site</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Custom design / brand match</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ Fully branded</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Their badge only</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Moderation control</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ You approve each one</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Platform decides</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Placement on pricing / CTA</td>
          <td class="vouch">✓ Anywhere you want</td>
          <td class="them">✗ Must link off-site</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Pricing</td>
          <td class="vouch">Free forever / $9 pro</td>
          <td class="them">$300–$1,000+/mo (vendor plans)</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section class="quote-section">
    <blockquote>"We put a SocialProof widget next to our pricing CTA and saw an immediate lift. Took 10 minutes to set up — I expected it to take a sprint."</blockquote>
    <cite>— Founder, B2B SaaS startup</cite>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
    <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card required.</p>
    <a class="btn-white" href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register">Create your free account →</a>
  </section>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
